ss=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ged1665702692140.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ged1665702692140.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ged1665702692140.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ged1665702692140\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ged1665702692140__uentseto_402214\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Make an occurrence of an entity parameter current.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ged1665702692140__topic_d119447e1_d119448e1_d119449e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ged1665702692140_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ged1665702692140__codeblock_lrf_qvs_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long uentseto (UHACT hEnt, long seqNr );</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ged1665702692140__topic_d85102e1_d85103e1_d85104e1_d85105e1_d85106e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277438e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ged1665702692140__parml_nmz_rvs_zvb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">hEnt</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Handle to the entity parameter.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Sequence number of the occurrence to be made current.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ged1665702692140__topic_d85107e1_d85108e1_d85109e1_d85110e1_d85111e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277438e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by uentseto</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">Success. The occurrence was made\n                        current.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">-66</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">Occurrence handle specified instead of entity\n                        handle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">-150</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">Hitlist not found</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">-165</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">The supplied handle is not valid.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__1\">-1203</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ged1665702692140__table_d14831e1_d14832e1_d14833e1__entry__2\">The occurrence number is out of range.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ged1665702692140__topic_d85112e1_d85113e1_d85114e1_d85115e1_d85116e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277438e169\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ged1665702692140__d5956e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">ucall</span></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ged1665702692140__topic_d85117e1_d85118e1_d85119e1_d85120e1_d85121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277438e181\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ged1665702692140__p_d119474e1_d119475e1_d119476e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uentseto</code> makes the specified occurrence of the specified entity parameter current. This function is very similar to the ProcScript function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>. In particular, it follows the same rules for the sequence number <var class=\"keyword varname\">seqNr</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ged1665702692140__p_d119477e1_d119478e1_d119479e1\">You cannot use <code class=\"ph codeph\">uentseto</code> with an occurrence parameter.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ged1665702692140__section_wvc_kqq_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d277438e205\">Example: uentcreo, uentremo, uentseto</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">uentcreo</code> to create 20\n               occurrences of an entity parameter, and then calls <code class=\"ph codeph\">uentremo</code> to\n               remove every other occurrence, so that only the even-numbered occurrences remain. It\n               then activates the operation SETENT in service ENTSRV, that prints the even-numbered\n               occurrences to the message frame. The entity ENT is defined with the following:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"ged1665702692140__codeblock_opq_xvs_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">PK CHAR(3)\nREC CHAR(20)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Operation SETENT is defined as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ged1665702692140_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ged1665702692140__codeblock_owv_yvs_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation setent\nparams\nentity ent : in;\nendparams\n$1 = 1\nsetocc \"ent\", $1\nwhile ( $status &gt;= 0 )\nputmess \"pk = %%pk rec = %%rec\"\n$1 = $1 + 1\nsetocc \"ent\", $1\nendwhile\nreturn 0\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The following is the 3GL code:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ged1665702692140_html_2\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ged1665702692140__codeblock_jjm_1ws_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nvoid set_ent ()\n{\nUHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */\nUHACT hOp, hEnt; /* Operation and entity handles */\nlong actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */\nint i; /* Occurrence loop counter */\nchar s1[80]; /* Work string */\nueopen(&amp;hEnv;) /* Get environment handle */\nuinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"ENTSRV\", 0, 0,\nUDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &amp;hIn, &amp;procErr);/*Instantiate service ENTSRV */\nuinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"SETENT\", 0, &amp;hOp);/*Instantiate operation SETENT */\nuprmgeth(hOp, 1, 0, &amp;hEnt); /* Get entity handle for ENT parameter */\nfor ( i=1 ; i&lt;=20; i++ ) /* Do 20 occurrences */\n{\nuentcreo(hEnt, -1); /* Add occurrence at the end */\nsprintf(s1, \"%d\", i); /* Generate PK data */\nustr2uf(hEnt, 1, s1); /* Fill PK */\nsprintf(s1, \"Record %d\", i);/* Generate REC data */\nustr2uf(hEnt, 2, s1); /* Fill REC */\n}\nfor ( i=1; /* Delete every other occurrence */\nuentremo(hEnt, i)==UACT_SUCCESS; i++ );\nuopract (hOp, &amp;actStatus, &amp;procErr); /* Activate ENTSRV */\nuinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Delete ENTSRV instance */\nufreeh (&amp;hOp;) /* Free SETENT operation handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hIn;) /* Free ENTSRV instance handle */\nufreeh (&amp;hEnv;) /* Free environment handle */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwd1665702691983.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uentcreo</a><p>Create an occurrence of an entity parameter, and make it current.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epa1665702692212.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uentgeto</a><p>Return the current occurrence number within an entity parameter.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527818\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527818\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uentseto Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Make an occurrence of an entity parameter current. Explain this code long uentseto (UHACT hEnt, long seqNr ); Copy Parameters hEnt Handle to the entity parameter. seqNr Sequence number of the occurrence to be made current. Return Values Table 1. Values returned by uentseto Value Meaning 0 Success. The occurrence was made current. -66 Occurrence handle specified instead of entity handle -150 Hitlist not found -165 The supplied handle is not valid. -1203 The occurrence number is out of range. Use Library: ucall Description uentseto makes the specified occurrence of the specified entity parameter current. This function is very similar to the ProcScript function setocc . In particular, it follows the same rules for the sequence number seqNr . You cannot use uentseto with an occurrence parameter. Example: uentcreo, uentremo, uentseto The following example uses uentcreo to create 20 occurrences of an entity parameter, and then calls uentremo to remove every other occurrence, so that only the even-numbered occurrences remain. It then activates the operation SETENT in service ENTSRV, that prints the even-numbered occurrences to the message frame. The entity ENT is defined with the following: PK CHAR(3) REC CHAR(20) Copy Operation SETENT is defined as follows: Explain this code operation setent params entity ent : in; endparams $1 = 1 setocc \"ent\", $1 while ( $status >= 0 ) putmess \"pk = %%pk rec = %%rec\" $1 = $1 + 1 setocc \"ent\", $1 endwhile return 0 end Copy The following is the 3GL code: Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> void set_ent () { UHACT hEnv, hIn; /* Environment and instance handle */ UHACT hOp, hEnt; /* Operation and entity handles */ long actStatus, procErr; /* Activation status and procerr */ int i; /* Occurrence loop counter */ char s1[80]; /* Work string */ ueopen(&hEnv;) /* Get environment handle */ uinstnew (hEnv, (UCHAR *)\"ENTSRV\", 0, 0, UDEFAULT_COMM_MODE, 0, &hIn, &procErr);/*Instantiate service ENTSRV */ uinstopr (hIn, (UCHAR *)\"SETENT\", 0, &hOp);/*Instantiate operation SETENT */ uprmgeth(hOp, 1, 0, &hEnt); /* Get entity handle for ENT parameter */ for ( i=1 ; i<=20; i++ ) /* Do 20 occurrences */ { uentcreo(hEnt, -1); /* Add occurrence at the end */ sprintf(s1, \"%d\", i); /* Generate PK data */ ustr2uf(hEnt, 1, s1); /* Fill PK */ sprintf(s1, \"Record %d\", i);/* Generate REC data */ ustr2uf(hEnt, 2, s1); /* Fill REC */ } for ( i=1; /* Delete every other occurrence */ uentremo(hEnt, i)==UACT_SUCCESS; i++ ); uopract (hOp, &actStatus, &procErr); /* Activate ENTSRV */ uinstdel (hIn, 0); /* Delete ENTSRV instance */ ufreeh (&hOp;) /* Free SETENT operation handle */ ufreeh (&hIn;) /* Free ENTSRV instance handle */ ufreeh (&hEnv;) /* Free environment handle */ } Copy Related Links uentcreo Create an occurrence of an entity parameter, and make it current. uentgeto Return the current occurrence number within an entity parameter. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}